From f3d51fd295e8d96ad11d522f822635db02686519 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ash Logan <ash@heyquark.com>
Date: Sat, 2 Nov 2024 19:28:47 +1100
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] wiiu: Add Espresso SMP erratum to atomic ops

Note I had to do a full make clean to get a proper build out of this
---
 arch/powerpc/include/asm/asm-espresso.h      | 18 ++++++++++++++++++
 arch/powerpc/include/asm/atomic.h            |  6 ++++++
 arch/powerpc/include/asm/bitops.h            |  7 +++++++
 arch/powerpc/include/asm/book3s/32/pgtable.h |  2 ++
 arch/powerpc/include/asm/cmpxchg.h           | 10 ++++++++++
 arch/powerpc/include/asm/edac.h              |  7 +++++--
 arch/powerpc/include/asm/futex.h             |  7 +++++--
 arch/powerpc/include/asm/qspinlock.h         |  2 ++
